    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your very own workmate cat, Purrounding</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unorganized wallpapers, file clutter...<br>Whether you're working, studying, or just staring at a blank screen, spend some time with your personalized cat through Purrounding!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244420/extras/ecd9dc88aa480a4a9766d9e3da1ac9f5.poster.avif?t=1736350631\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244420/extras/ecd9dc88aa480a4a9766d9e3da1ac9f5.webm?t=1736350631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244420/extras/ecd9dc88aa480a4a9766d9e3da1ac9f5.mp4?t=1736350631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left alone, the cat will walk on your taskbar, curl up like a loaf of bread, and just hang out on your screen. You can use your mouse to interact with your cat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can customize your cat to your liking. Change their fur color, eye color, and even add different patterns to make your cat unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why not have a clock with a Pomodoro timer when you need to focus?<br>You can also listen to soothing lo-fi music on the radio to help you focus on your work. Customize and arrange your screen with a variety of other furniture pieces.</p>",
